+#
+# Macro to add for using GNU gettext.
+# Ulrich Drepper <drepper@cygnus.com>, 1995, 1996
+#
+# Modified to never use included libintl. 
+# Owen Taylor <otaylor@redhat.com>, 12/15/1998
